s/meta/color}};\" | 12\n| [[File:Joschka Fischer.jpg|60px]]\n| {{sortname|Joschka|Fischer}}\n| 12 April 1948\n|\n| 27 October 1998\n| {{age|1948|4|12|1998|10|27}}\n| 22 November 2005\n| {{age|1948|4|12|2005|11|22}}\n| {{age in days|1998|10|27|2005|11|22}}\n| [[Alliance '90/The Greens|Green]]\n| [[Federal Foreign Office|Foreign Affairs]]\n| style=\"background:{{Social Democratic Party of Germany/meta/color}}; color:white\" |\n| [[Cabinet Schr\u00f6der I|Schr\u00f6der I]] \u2022 [[Cabinet Schr\u00f6der II|II]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Social Democratic Party of Germany/meta/color}}; color:white\" | 13\n| [[File:FranzM\u00fcntefering mw1.jpg|60px]]\n| {{sortname|Franz|M\u00fcntefering}}\n| 16 January 1940\n|\n| 22 November 2005\n| {{age|1940|1|16|2005|11|22}}\n| 21 November 2007\n| {{age|1940|1|16|2007|11|21}}\n| {{age in days|2005|11|22|2007|11|21}}\n| SPD\n| [[Federal Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs (Germany)|Labour and Social Affairs]]\n| style=\"background:{{CDU/CSU/meta/color}}; color:white\" |\n| [[Cabinet Merkel I|Merkel I]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Social Democratic Party of Germany/meta/color}}; color:white\" | 14\n| [[File:Frank-Walter Steinmeier Feb 2014 (cropped).jpg|60px]]\n| {{sortname|Frank-Walter|Steinmeier}}\n| 5 January 1956\n|\n| 21 November 2007\n| {{age|1956|1|5|2007|11|21}}\n| 27 October 2009\n| {{age|1956|1|5|2009|10|27}}\n| {{age in days|2007|11|21|2009|10|27}}\n| SPD\n| [[Federal Foreign Office|Foreign Affairs]]\n| style=\"background:{{CDU/CSU/meta/color}}; color:white\" |\n| [[Cabinet Merkel I|Merkel I]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Free Democratic Party (Germany)/meta/color}};\" | 15\n| [[File:Guido westerwelle.jpg|60px]]\n| {{sortname|Guido|Westerwelle}}\n| 27 December 1961\n| 18 March 2016\n| 28 October 2009\n| {{age|1961|12|27|2009|10|28}}\n| 16 May 2011\n| {{age|1961|12|27|2011|5|16}}\n| {{age in days|2009|10|28|2011|5|16}}\n| FDP\n| [[Federal Foreign Office|Foreign Affairs]]\n| style=\"background:{{CDU/CSU/meta/color}}; color: