cess-date=2020-03-03|via=ScotlandsPlaces}}\n*{{Cite web|url=http://www.thessvlbhistory.co.uk/pdf/A%20%20SHORT%20%20HISTORY%20of%20lsa%20equipment.pdf|title=A Short History of the Life Saving Apparatus|last=|first=|date=|website=A History of South Shields Volunteer Life Brigade|format=PDF|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-03-04|ref={{harvid|SSVLB|}}}}\n*{{Cite magazine|last=|first=|date=April 1978|title=Award to \"Elinor Viking\" heroes - Department of Trade Rescue Shield for 1977|url=http://reardonsmithships.co.uk/rslnewsletter099.pdf#page=3|magazine=Reardon Smith Line Limited Newsletters|issue=99|page=3|access-date=2020-03-23|ref={{harvid|Reardon Smith|1978}}}}\n*{{Cite web|url=http://canmore.org.uk/site/115531|title=Ben Doran: Helligoblo, Ve Skerries, Atlantic|website=[[Canmore (database)|Canmore]]|url-status=live|access-date=2020-04-06|ref={{harvid|Canmore - Ben Doran|}}}}\n*{{Cite news|last=|first=|url=https://www.britishnewspaperarchive.co.uk/viewer/bl/0000666/19090515/153/0004|title=Crew Landed at Olnafirth|date=1909-05-15|work=[[The Shetland Times]]|access-date=2020-04-12|url-status=live|page=4|ref={{harvid|Shetland Times|1909}}|url-access=subscription|via=The [[British Newspaper Archive]]}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://www.shetland.org/things/outdoor/diving|title=Diving|last=|first=|date=|website=Shetland.org|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-06|ref={{harvid|Shetland.org|}}}}\n*{{Cite web|url=https://canmore.org.uk/site/238834|title=Elinor Viking: Reverack, Ve Skerries, Atlantic|website=[[Canmore (database)|Canmore]]|url-status=live|access-date=2020-04-06|ref={{harvid|Canmore - Elinor Viking|}}}}\n*{{Cite news|url=https://www.thegazette.co.uk/London/issue/47582/supplement/8045|title=Honours and Awards|date=1978-07-04|work=The London Gazette|access-date=2020-04-06|url-status=live|publisher=[[Her Majesty's Stationery Office]]|issue=47582|pages=8045-8046|isbn=0 11 657582 4|ref={{harvid|London Gazette|1978}}}}\n